Package io.grpc.transport.netty

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Http2Negotiator.Negotiation
    A Netty-based negotiation that provides an pre-configured ChannelInitializer for to negotiate the requested protocol.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Http2Negotiator
    A utility class that provides support methods for negotiating the use of HTTP/2 with the remote endpoint.
    NettyChannelBuilder
    A builder to help simplify construction of channels using the Netty transport.
    NettyServer
    Implementation of the Service interface for a Netty-based server.
    NettyServerBuilder
    A builder to help simplify the construction of a Netty-based GRPC server.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NegotiationType
    Identifies the negotiation used for starting up HTTP/2.
